comment.narrative:
1.	National GHG inventory report in English and Georgian completed, printed and submitted to the Ministry of Environment and Natural resources Protection of Georgia;
2.	Georgia’s First Biennial Update report to the UNFCCC with all respective parts in English and Georgian completed, printed and submitted to the Ministry of Environment and Natural resources Protection of Georgia;
3.	Trainings to the Domestic MRV verifiers provided;
4.	Short glossary on climate change terminology prepared;
5.	Study on lessons learned and comparative analysis of national circumstances during Georgia’s reporting process to the UNFCCC carried out;
6.	Support on domestic MRV system establishment in Georgia provided.

